project:
- Set CBoardWidth , CBoardHeight , CBoardSpc in [b]CreatorSheet[/b]

- Left click on a spot to make a dot 

- Right click on a dot to remove it

- Number keys on keyboard will change the dots and strings color while mouse is over on them

- Touch and drag on a dot to make a line, then connect it to another dot

- When you done with the shape, click on [b]MainShape Done[/b] button. Then you can drag the dots and mess the shape

- in the end, click on [b]Generate[/b] , then copy the code and paste it in [b]GameSheet > Levels[/b]
